<H2>
Undergraduate Studies
</H2>

<center><img src="sy16985.thm.jpg"></center>


<p>
The sub-department currently provides three courses:

<UL>
<li>A third year core course on "Atmospheric Physics"; the first half
of this is on Climate Physics and the second half is on <a
HREF="http://www.atm.ox.ac.uk/user/andrews/fluids.html">Fluid
Flows</a>.

<li>A short option on <a href = "http://www.atm.ox.ac.uk/user/read/chaos/chaos.html">   Chaos, Chance and Predictability</a>.
  
<li>A fourth year major option on the <a
HREF="http://www.atm.ox.ac.uk/user/andrews/option.html">"Physics
of Atmospheres and Oceans"</a>
</UL>

Funding to work in the sub-department during the summer vacation is available from 
 <a HREF="http://www.rmets.org/pdf/regs_undergrad.pdf"> The Royal Meteorological Society</a>.
